column16: Yonder Alonso grounds into a double play, shortstop Didi Gregorius to first baseman Mark Teixeira.   Jed Lowrie to 3rd.    Khris Davis out at 2nd.
Khris Davis singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.   Billy Butler scores.    Stephen Vogt scores.    Jed Lowrie to 2nd.
Jed Lowrie walks.   Billy Butler to 3rd.    Stephen Vogt to 2nd.
Stephen Vogt singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.   Billy Butler to 2nd.
Billy Butler singles on a line drive to right fielder Carlos Beltran.
